The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 8th February,
2001, Shri Syed Shahnawaz Hussain, relinquished the charge of the office of
Minister of State in the Ministry of Human Resource Development and assumed
the charge of the office of Minister of State (Independent charge) of the Ministry of
Coal.
